hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: A packet of envelopes seroquel coupon It’s essentially a straightforward paper trail, albeit one whose linearity is cleverly disguised for the most part. Yet if much can be explained away by the messy business of moving house, the location of some key items is a little contrived, temporarily breaking the spell. Meanwhile, the player’s involvement can often spoil that carefully cultivated atmosphere: you’ll rummage clumsily around for the next piece of the puzzle, picking up meaningless detritus while missing key clues, and just about every new room sees you fumble for the light switch upon entering. (This is not a game to be played in daylight hours, not least because the house is almost comically gloomy.).
